# Section 4 — Complete Project Folder Structure

---

# 4.1 Introduction

Understanding the project folder structure is essential before diving into the implementation.

The Study Abroad Finder project was intentionally organized to separate:

- Presentation Layer
- Backend Layer
- AI Layer
- MCP Servers
- Reports
- Deployment
- Configuration

Each folder has a single responsibility.

This modular organization makes the application easier to understand, maintain, debug, and extend.

