# 4.9 reports/

```
reports/
```

Purpose

Stores generated Markdown reports.

Examples

```
AI_Germany_Report.md

Machine_Learning_USA.md

Technical_University_of_Munich.md
```

Local Development

```
reports/
```

exists inside the project folder.

Docker Deployment

Reports are stored inside

```
/app/reports
```

inside the container.

Important

Render containers are ephemeral.

Reports survive only until the container is restarted.

Future versions should store reports in

- Amazon S3

or

- Google Cloud Storage

or

- Azure Blob Storage

or

Render Persistent Disk

